WEBVTT

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:20.530
A Sahaja yogi is a person who has  total satisfaction, 

00:00:20.530 --> 00:00:23.288
who has achieved, whose pure desire has been fulfilled, 

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:27.837
because Kundalini is the power of pure desire. 

00:00:27.837 --> 00:00:30.703
In a person whose pure desire has been fulfilled, 

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:36.746
one whose power of pure desire has shown its miracles completely, there is no desire left. 

00:00:36.746 --> 00:00:39.713
A person who is fully satisfied is a real Sahaja yogi. 

00:00:41.014 --> 00:00:46.486
If there is any unfulfilled desire still remaining, then it means that the awakening of the Kundalini is not complete. 

00:00:46.486 --> 00:00:51.200
You have not yet become a fully-fledged Sahaja yogi. 

00:00:52.320 --> 00:01:00.732
It is so surprising that even without becoming a proper Sahaja yogi, blessings keep coming, and miracles keep happening. 

00:01:00.732 --> 00:01:03.577
You keep getting the benefits. You continue to be aware that 

00:01:03.577 --> 00:01:09.220
“We are moving, everything is in place, things are happening, and we are progressing”. 

00:01:10.975 --> 00:01:14.904
But the biggest blessing for a Sahaja yogi is that he gets the ability to give, and he

00:01:14.904 --> 00:01:18.464
And he not only gives; he enjoys giving, which is a very unique joy, 

00:01:18.761 --> 00:01:25.834
and that joy that you can never get from any worldly things. 

00:01:26.133 --> 00:01:34.391
And all other such blessings cannot bring about this kind of joy. 

00:01:34.862 --> 00:01:39.126
The biggest blessing is that your power of the Guru Principle increases, 

00:01:39.126 --> 00:01:42.531
and you develop the ability to give it to others. 

00:01:42.860 --> 00:01:50.798
When you gain this ability, then understand that the work of Mother is complete, and now your work has commenced. 

00:01:51.409 --> 00:01:53.424
That state is not achieved until 

00:01:53.851 --> 00:01:56.911
you have made the effort and you have become. 

00:01:56.911 --> 00:02:03.872
This is the only condition of Sahaja Yoga, which I say as a Mother, 

00:02:03.872 --> 00:02:09.166
that I do My best not to leave anything wanting. 

00:02:09.166 --> 00:02:14.678
From My side. I do as much as possible to see that nothing is incomplete from My side 

00:02:14.678 --> 00:02:21.673
so that on account of Me, My children should not have any shortcomings.

00:02:21.673 --> 00:02:24.832
But your penance [tapasya] is also important.

00:02:24.832 --> 00:02:30.266
Without that, no work can be done.But it should not be that such penance is aggressive [ugra] or painful [santapta]).

00:02:30.266 --> 00:02:36.156
It is a peaceful penance. There is  nothing hard in this penance. It is not a laborious penance.

00:02:36.156 --> 00:02:40.657
In the same manner, a Sahaja yogi has to go about with a lot of wisdom and be a sensible person, 

00:02:40.657 --> 00:02:46.115
and should take up responsibility in a way that “We are wise people”.

00:02:46.115 --> 00:02:53.116
The inner wisdom that we have is our quality, our symbol, our custom. 

00:02:53.116 --> 00:02:58.182
The wisdom within us, that we should present on ourselves, like somebody proudly applies a vermilion [tilak], 

00:02:58.182 --> 00:03:01.105
we  have to present our wisdom like with a tilak. 

00:03:01.858 --> 00:03:04.000
And we are wise. 

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:09.111
The meaning of wisdom is that a person who is wise does not go in for tantrums and does not get upset. 

00:03:09.111 --> 00:03:14.633
He does not slip onto small things and does not comment that, “This is not good. That is not good.” 

00:03:14.633 --> 00:03:17.226
He speaks with wisdom. 

00:03:17.226 --> 00:03:19.937
This is a sign of greatness, a sign of maturity. 

00:03:19.937 --> 00:03:24.359
In Sahaja Yoga, a person who cannot be mature is not fit for Sahaja Yoga. 

00:03:24.359 --> 00:03:28.808
You have to become mature, and wise as well. 

00:03:30.422 --> 00:03:35.570
It seems like a very difficult task, but it is actually not so much. 

00:03:35.570 --> 00:03:39.055
We have seen small children in Sahaja Yoga. They are very wise, 

00:03:39.055 --> 00:03:42.602
and they understand everything wisely. 

00:03:42.963 --> 00:03:48.000
In the same manner, you also have a tilak of wisdom that you are now a Sahaja yogi,

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:53.273
and wise also, and this is a subject of your Mother’s honour.

00:03:53.273 --> 00:04:00.557
Those who are not sensible – people will say that their Mother [Guru] has not taught them anything and not good. 

00:04:01.005 --> 00:04:04.771
They call Her Adi Shakti, and some of these children are not good. 

00:04:07.351 --> 00:04:12.610
With this wisdom in mind you should look at yourself that “We have a responsibility. 

00:04:12.610 --> 00:04:19.428
It is essential that we become wise people before the world”. 

00:04:19.428 --> 00:04:27.141
we are a big personality. Maturity means having a kind of paternal feeling, a fatherly feeling, a motherly feeling. 

00:04:27.141 --> 00:04:31.446
You need to look after the new seekers with this feeling, 

00:04:31.446 --> 00:04:36.702
having love towards them like the love your Mother has for you. You should love them like that. 

00:04:36.702 --> 00:04:42.000
If I would have thought that the people of the world are absolutely useless, 

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:45.387
then would we have been able to work out Sahaja Yoga? 

00:04:46.075 --> 00:04:50.555
And if I only go on comparing Myself, then I am alone in this world. 

00:04:50.555 --> 00:04:54.384
With whom can I compare Myself ? 

00:04:54.772 --> 00:04:59.227
But that question does not arise at all. 

00:04:59.227 --> 00:05:01.856
Here it is like how many can we bring in to our shelter? 

00:05:01.856 --> 00:05:07.392
Now our numbers are less. In this shelter, who do we bring? Who can we keep? This is the concern. 

00:05:07.392 --> 00:05:11.572
In the same manner, in your attention there should be maturity with love. 

00:05:11.572 --> 00:05:15.960
It should not be such that some people call you a very great person. 

00:05:16.169 --> 00:05:23.691
I prefer you should have very simple, Sahaja love within you. 

00:05:24.348 --> 00:05:30.501
And in that simple Sahaja love, you should have a fatherly feeling, and a feeling of understanding. 

00:05:31.134 --> 00:05:34.024
I have a lot of confidence in you, 

00:05:34.681 --> 00:05:37.116
a lot of confidence In any matter, 

00:05:37.658 --> 00:05:40.015
whether it is the matter of money, or your wisdom. 

00:05:41.794 --> 00:05:45.569
I always think that My children can never be unwise. 

00:05:46.544 --> 00:05:55.390
Sometimes they are, but I have full faith that you all are very wise and of very high quality. 

00:05:56.330 --> 00:05:59.642
Love should be pure. Pure love. 

00:05:59.642 --> 00:06:02.845
What is pure love? 

00:06:03.173 --> 00:06:20.972
Pure love is that which has no greed, nor does it have lust; no greed, and no lust, and there is no type of filth. 

00:06:20.972 --> 00:06:23.462
It goes on flowing endlessly. 

00:06:24.198 --> 00:06:28.369
The light of this pure love should flow from within us. 

00:06:29.027 --> 00:06:32.117
This pure desire should be within us. 

00:06:32.378 --> 00:06:39.175
When this starts happening, then you will become an admired Sahaja yogi – not before that. 

00:06:41.565 --> 00:06:46.554
And this speciality of becoming should be given due attention. 

00:06:46.554 --> 00:06:53.351
Today, you will say, “Mother, please make this all right. Mother, please make that all right.” OK, I will do it. 

00:06:53.351 --> 00:06:57.091
I will do it. But you will not become something. 

00:06:57.450 --> 00:07:01.643
A child will say, “Mother, please give this to me.” OK, child, take it. You want it, take it. 

00:07:01.643 --> 00:07:03.708
But you have not become anything special. 

00:07:04.695 --> 00:07:06.549
You have not achieved anything. 

00:07:07.923 --> 00:07:11.702
You just went on running after Mother. What is the benefit? 

00:07:13.715 --> 00:07:21.393
Whatever Mother wants to make of you, if you do not become that, then even Mother’s pure desire will not be fulfilled. 

00:07:21.393 --> 00:07:28.518
it's a very strange thing that my pure desire from within is that you should become. 

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:34.273
And you have pure desire from within that you want to become something. 

00:07:34.273 --> 00:07:38.724
When we are in unison like this, let us just be with pure desire. 

00:07:39.614 --> 00:07:45.095
And the first thing that is required to be with pure desire is pure love. 

00:07:45.095 --> 00:07:48.828
And in order to bring purity in us, we have to purify our attention. 

00:07:50.322 --> 00:07:58.081
When you look at others, you should have an appreciative temperament, 

00:07:58.081 --> 00:08:08.903
blank

00:08:09.617 --> 00:08:22.064
When you look at others, you should have an appreciative temperament, and you should have the strength to love everyone, 

00:08:22.273 --> 00:08:25.975
Only one thing should attract: another person’s spirit. 

00:08:25.975 --> 00:08:30.668
That is the only thing that gives joy. 

00:08:31.325 --> 00:08:37.419
By keeping our attention outside, our attention gets entangled. 

00:08:37.419 --> 00:08:42.584
The attention should become deep, penetrating, deep. 

00:08:50.420 --> 00:08:55.729
Now those days are gone now, now Satya Yuga has started.

00:08:57.464 --> 00:09:06.000
In Satya Yuga I assure you anybody who is not blessed by Rajalakshmi

00:09:08.112 --> 00:09:17.400
will have to go to jail or will have to leave the seat, will be thrown away

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:28.927
or will be as they say, “Doubly dying go to the waste, dust”.  It has to be. They’ll be all exposed,

00:09:29.450 --> 00:09:31.299
whatever tricks they may try.

00:09:34.825 --> 00:09:42.113
And they will have the consequence of being artificially the rulers.

00:09:45.528 --> 00:09:47.212
But a genuineness

00:09:49.769 --> 00:09:52.021
is the sign that the queen

00:09:55.047 --> 00:10:05.584
of blessings, the goddess of
Rajalakshmi, is residing in that person.

00:10:11.341 --> 00:10:18.133
In Satya Yuga it will happen I’m sure. But even in Sahaja Yoga

00:10:18.518 --> 00:10:25.711
I find people doing politics sometimes, I was amazed! People think politics means

00:10:28.072 --> 00:10:34.015
keeping groups, making groups, telling things from here to there, there to there.

00:10:35.061 --> 00:10:39.087
That shows you lack collectivity.

00:10:41.852 --> 00:10:47.117
A person who is a Sahaja Yogi will try to cement everyone together

00:10:48.246 --> 00:10:52.464
because the power lies in collectivity.

00:10:55.278 --> 00:11:05.610
To break the collectivity for anything is very dangerous
for that person as well as for others.

00:11:09.191 --> 00:11:20.803
So now you have entered into the kingdom of God, you are now sitting in the court of God Almighty.

00:11:23.774 --> 00:11:33.781
Here, of course, as courtiers you have to dress up well, sit
properly, should take up your seats.

00:11:34.222 --> 00:11:41.013
You have to be systematic and above board
because you are Sahaja Yogis.

00:11:42.225 --> 00:11:51.408
You are not ordinary people. You are special
people. How many people in this world are going to be Sahaja Yogi?

00:11:54.327 --> 00:12:01.499
You are special people, so try to make yourself

00:12:03.867 --> 00:12:10.629
such beautiful instruments of Rajalakshmi
that people when they will see you

00:12:12.282 --> 00:12:16.737
they will vote for you and tomorrow you will rule the world.

00:12:28.950 --> 00:12:35.847
All that was first a gross attraction becomes very subtle attraction.

00:12:36.775 --> 00:12:39.336
They start using it.

00:12:41.841 --> 00:12:43.841
In both ways it acts.

00:12:44.294 --> 00:12:56.480
With some people it may act in a way that you want to enjoy the game of power,

00:12:57.373 --> 00:13:00.346
those who have missed it or those who know how to use it.

00:13:01.007 --> 00:13:10.215
There could be another type who are the ones who think they have always suffered and they are suffering now also.

00:13:12.673 --> 00:13:16.141
There can be another type of a group
of people,

00:13:19.479 --> 00:13:28.143
who, when they come to Sahaja Yoga, they have complications of
emotions.

00:13:29.768 --> 00:13:36.398
I know of some people, I’ve heard, that they felt attraction for a man or a woman

00:13:36.898 --> 00:13:41.028
and they started behaving in that fashion – after coming to Sahaja
Yoga!

00:13:44.594 --> 00:13:47.275
Sometimes, the attraction to money,

00:13:48.421 --> 00:13:53.522
attraction to greed and lust becomes subtler.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:14:00.153
So, the Mahamaya being the subtler force, it’s the subtlest of all,

00:14:00.606 --> 00:14:04.880
which you
cannot understand and can’t explain through your brains at all,

00:14:05.844 --> 00:14:10.807
acts and just stupefies.

00:14:11.523 --> 00:14:17.402
It stupefies. Unless and until that is done, they cannot stop it,

00:14:17.402 --> 00:14:22.885
they cannot cut themselves away. They, in a subtler way, they remain the same,

00:14:24.824 --> 00:14:27.386
but not aware of it.

00:14:29.247 --> 00:14:33.410
People who are miserly become miserly,

00:14:34.567 --> 00:14:39.082
in a very subtle way, in a very sophisticated way, but they are miserly.

00:14:41.131 --> 00:14:46.303
Those who are dominating become
dominating in a subtler way.

00:14:46.835 --> 00:14:51.358
Those who are murmuring are doing it in a subtler way;

00:14:51.771 --> 00:14:53.964
complaining are doing in a subtler way.

00:14:56.294 --> 00:15:02.238
And that’s why the Mahamaya acts.
First of all, it stupefies you, completely.

00:15:05.559 --> 00:15:13.643
So, you realize that whatever you think or
react to something, to certain situations,

00:15:15.095 --> 00:15:21.237
it’s a Maya, is just a hallucination created.

00:15:23.548 --> 00:15:25.548
Now for example we’ll take

00:15:26.263 --> 00:15:31.620
the second chapter of Gita, which is written about a
“sthita prajna”. The one who is a yogi, who is a Sahaja Yogi,

00:15:32.603 --> 00:15:38.923
to him, everything should be Samaan: whether somebody insults you or whether somebody loves you;

00:15:39.822 --> 00:15:43.739
whether somebody discards you, whether somebody accepts you;

00:15:43.852 --> 00:15:48.352
whether somebody is generous to you or whether somebody is not generous to you.

00:15:49.686 --> 00:15:53.310
to a sthita prajna, it makes no difference. He’s above everything,

00:15:53.310 --> 00:16:00.696
he is floating in the boat of joy. Nothing can disturb such a person.

00:16:00.696 --> 00:16:08.744
That’s the sign. If your joy can be disturbed by anything else that means you are not yet a full Sahaja Yogi.

00:16:13.567 --> 00:16:14.774
So the judgement (laughing)

00:16:16.573 --> 00:16:22.253
of a sahaja yogi doesn’t come from what he claims but what he achieves.

00:16:25.755 --> 00:16:31.759
I’ve seen some sahaja yogis are extremely arrogant, also.
Extremely arrogant.

00:16:31.983 --> 00:16:35.948
Think no end of themselves. All that is there.

00:16:36.594 --> 00:16:42.021
So many sahaja
yogis I have seen of that kind, that, they are very very arrogant

00:16:42.246 --> 00:16:48.839
and that they try
to make a big show out of what great people they are –

00:16:50.666 --> 00:16:54.570
Humpty Dumpties as they call it.   Alright, but

00:16:55.802 --> 00:17:01.467
what [about] a sahaja yogi, who is not like that, what is his style is?

00:17:02.365 --> 00:17:08.595
He’ll just watch, he’ll witness the whole thing, just enjoy and laugh at
what is happening.

00:17:08.929 --> 00:17:13.766
“What is this man talking like this. What’s the sense of his
talking like this.”

00:17:15.571 --> 00:17:17.571
 A person who is a sahaja yogi,

00:17:18.731 --> 00:17:22.379
is a gem, a gem,

00:17:23.804 --> 00:17:30.576
and gem for which you take him to anywhere, to any place, people will say “He’s a gem.”

00:17:41.377 --> 00:17:53.551
My own style is this, that when I see a person or a sahaja yogi anywhere,

00:17:54.190 --> 00:17:58.877
first thing I go inside Myself - first thing,

00:17:59.664 --> 00:18:02.640
I don’t know if you can do that but I can.

00:18:03.582 --> 00:18:08.201
And
then I see that person in a very different perspective

00:18:09.208 --> 00:18:12.157
and understand. Because all
these powers are with you also.

00:18:12.846 --> 00:18:15.844
It is not My powers only, you all have these
powers,

00:18:15.844 --> 00:18:21.692
but only difference between you and Me is that I have all faith in Myself
and you have no faith in yourself.

00:18:30.742 --> 00:18:44.548
So we are at a crossing roads where we have to understand who will go higher
and who will go lower.

00:18:45.100 --> 00:18:50.230
We have to find out who is the one who is going to
achieve something,

00:18:50.230 --> 00:18:52.909
and where am I compared to that person?

00:18:55.717 --> 00:19:01.140
It’s said that you have to suffer, you have to do this and you have to do that – nothing of the kind,

00:19:01.140 --> 00:19:04.788
by God’s grace, nothing of that kind.

00:19:05.532 --> 00:19:08.606
So, now, what is it?

00:19:10.466 --> 00:19:19.172
What will happen to a sahaja yogi? How will you know who is
a sahaja yogi?

00:19:20.275 --> 00:19:26.640
How will you know who is just putting a lip service?

00:19:27.931 --> 00:19:38.101
Only way is that you evolve, you become like a mirror and you see for yourself what sort of a person he is,

00:19:39.147 --> 00:19:43.337
and also you see yourself, what you are.

00:20:04.328 --> 00:20:10.377
But if you can acquire other qualities also it will be a good idea.

00:20:13.819 --> 00:20:20.699
And that’s what I think should be the attitude towards Sahaja Yoga: that no work is below our dignity.

00:20:20.699 --> 00:20:22.525
For some people have such ego,

00:20:22.800 --> 00:20:28.202
“Oh I’m coming there why not I have a room?” Such stupid people have nothing to do with Sahaja Yoga,  I tell you.

00:20:28.715 --> 00:20:35.700
“I must have a special room!” “Why shouldn’t I have this?” This is absolute sign of a stupid fellow;

00:20:36.672 --> 00:20:44.415
is absolutely a sign of a person who has never known what is comfort, never known what is money, never known

00:20:47.307 --> 00:20:50.603
what is luxury. It’s something cheapish like a beggar

00:20:52.567 --> 00:21:00.811
who just starts demanding, “Give me five shillings!” then he asks for one hundred shillings and this and that.

00:21:00.811 --> 00:21:05.557
All these things – the one who asks for things is not a king.

00:21:08.094 --> 00:21:12.531
The one who accepts whatever comes their way is the real king because he’s mastered it.

00:21:17.890 --> 00:21:25.562
This is what is the right attitude. That’s what a Sahaja Yogi has to be. [The one] who goes on grudging, grumbling

00:21:25.727 --> 00:21:31.605
about small, small things is not a Sahaja Yogi. Sahaja Yogi is a king:

00:21:32.238 --> 00:21:39.315
he gives, gives Realisation, the utmost, the highest.

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:50.370
It doesn’t mean all plump people are good.

00:21:51.499 --> 00:21:57.592
We always logically think that plump people are, if Mother says so, then plump people are good. It‘s not the point,

00:21:57.592 --> 00:22:03.744
 the inner side of it, I am saying, the inner side of it, is just the opposite.

00:22:04.763 --> 00:22:14.154
Inner side of it is absolutely beautiful and absolutely full of love,

00:22:14.154 --> 00:22:15.985
affection and warmth.

00:22:16.701 --> 00:22:23.550
A person who doesn’t have these things is a sign of a person who is not a Sahaja Yogi,

00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:35.665
first of all. A person who is very loud, talks loudly, speaks loudly, laughs at wrong places must be half mad

00:22:35.665 --> 00:22:37.719
but cannot be a Sahaja Yogi.

00:22:44.953 --> 00:22:53.840
So one has to understand that our main object is to reach that state of doubtless awareness

00:22:53.840 --> 00:22:59.022
where we all the time absolutely enjoying ourselves.

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:08.883
{Hindi} the spirit is satisfied by spirit.

00:23:09.819 --> 00:23:24.276
So the enjoyment by the spirit，of the spirit. Then what is there to complain because your spirit is enlightened.

00:23:25.986 --> 00:23:32.911
The more you grow in Sahaja yoga you will be amazed to see how you enjoy collectivity.

00:23:33.241 --> 00:23:42.703
If the person cannot enjoy collectivity ，he thinks he is very highly placed，he has a special job or he is something great

00:23:42.703 --> 00:23:52.552
and he cannot talk with other sahaja yogis with the same level the same love then he is not a sahaja yogi.

00:23:54.000 --> 00:24:03.549
So now we understand that it for a Sahaja yogi it is important to keep to the central path all the time.

00:24:04.072 --> 00:24:11.483
Through meditation in the evening you can come into the central path and to try to stay there

00:24:11.483 --> 00:24:16.651
 in the Nirvichar Samadhi means thoughtless awareness.

00:24:17.890 --> 00:24:30.685
That state of thoughtless awareness does not allow any of these things to disturb.

00:24:31.677 --> 00:24:34.507
So as sahaja yogi has to meditate

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:44.779
to achieve that state of thoughtless awareness for a quite a long duration.

00:24:53.344 --> 00:25:01.770
So when you are so much tied down with your watch, that means you are not tied down with your Spirit.

00:25:02.982 --> 00:25:06.989
So a Sahaja Yogi, if he sees watch, then he’s not a Sahaja Yogi.

00:25:10.790 --> 00:25:16.841
But the other side could be that the Sahaja Yogis are never in time where they have to be.

00:25:27.444 --> 00:25:31.556
‘First will be the last’, Christ has said. ‘First will be the last’

00:25:32.287 --> 00:25:40.713
because the first (ones) come as if thinking that they have something great, that they have shown some great thing.

00:25:41.402 --> 00:25:49.032
But they do not know what is to be achieved; the innocence, the simplicity, the overpowering of your body –

00:25:50.908 --> 00:25:55.485
If your body tries to overpower you, you are no more a Sahaja Yogi.

00:25:56.146 --> 00:26:01.085
If your mind tries to overpower you then you are no more a Sahaja Yogi.

00:26:01.779 --> 00:26:08.452
If your heart tries to overpower you then also, you are not a Sahaja Yogi.

00:26:09.168 --> 00:26:14.731
But through all these three instruments, through these three instruments,

00:26:15.061 --> 00:26:19.881
you should work as if you are the master of these three instruments and not the slave 
of these three.

00:26:21.837 --> 00:26:27.870
This is a very very important thing because Sahaja Yoga has too many blessings.

00:26:29.659 --> 00:26:35.073
It gives you all kinds of prosperity, all kinds of beautiful blessings,

00:26:36.331 --> 00:26:45.798
all kinds of protections, miracles happen in your life. But we take Sahaja Yoga for granted.

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:58.760
All right. We are Sahaja Yogis.

00:26:58.880 --> 00:27:04.159
so what do we think about? !
First thing we’ll think, “Now, today is a puja,

00:27:04.159 --> 00:27:08.120
What should I wear?"

00:27:09.360 --> 00:27:14.320
Then, “I haven’t yet pressed my clothes,”
or, “my sari’s not all right. I have to

00:27:14.320 --> 00:27:19.520
match it,” and, “How to dress up."
All these frivolous things first come to

00:27:19.520 --> 00:27:25.200
our house, our brain.
Or in the morning, when you get up in

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:29.080
your ashrams or anywhere,

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:32.840
what do you think?

00:27:34.320 --> 00:27:42.960
If it was Christ,
He would say, “I am sleeping still?

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:49.120
I have to meditate!
I have to be one

00:27:49.120 --> 00:27:53.919
with the Divine!”
He would not say, “No, no, the Divine will

00:27:53.919 --> 00:27:59.039
look after, it’s all right. The Divine
will meditate for me!”

00:27:59.039 --> 00:28:04.960
“After all, Paramchaitanya, it has to
meditate. Why should we meditate? We are

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:08.200
all Sahaj Yogis.

00:28:08.480 --> 00:28:12.960
“Everything is sahaj, so let the Divine
meditate for us!” “We can’t get up

00:28:12.960 --> 00:28:20.600
in the morning. It’s difficult.
We can’t, you see, just can’t.”

00:28:22.159 --> 00:28:27.039
But then you can’t be a Sahaj Yogi!
You are supposed to be connected with all

00:28:27.039 --> 00:28:33.760
the deities, not only Christ,
and here you can’t even get out of your bed

00:28:33.760 --> 00:28:38.679
to meditate;

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:46.520
while all the deities are already up there,
waiting for you to get up, that’s all.

00:28:48.399 --> 00:28:54.960
And they can’t understand
what’s happening to these Sahaj Yogis.

00:28:54.960 --> 00:28:59.600
“How can they be so low?
After all, Mother must have given them

00:28:59.600 --> 00:29:03.360
Realisation thinking them to be
something great. How did they get

00:29:03.360 --> 00:29:06.360
Realisation？

00:29:06.399 --> 00:29:11.279
They’re so ordinary, so mundane, so useless.

00:29:11.279 --> 00:29:18.279
The deities start wondering,
“Why Mother gave them Realisation?”

00:29:19.120 --> 00:29:23.120
Because a person who cannot enjoy his
meditation

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:26.840
cannot be a Sahaj Yogi.

00:29:30.616 --> 00:29:39.181
That’s the first sign of a Sahaj Yogi: 
that he looks forward to that time when he can meditate.

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:50.159
That is the time that you are really in
connection

00:29:50.159 --> 00:29:55.440
with the Divine and you enjoy the most,
and whenever I get a chance, I go into it.

00:29:55.440 --> 00:30:01.279
I find it so difficult to come out of it!
I mean, for today it happened to Me,

00:30:01.279 --> 00:30:06.919
I was first thinking that I will have to struggle out
for this puja.

00:30:09.360 --> 00:30:13.120
I’ll have to work it out.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:19.279
I don’t know how I will get out of this
meditative mode.

00:30:19.279 --> 00:30:23.080
May God bless you!
